cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on improving real-time segmentation frameworks for robot perception data, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) category. The paper also heavily relies on computer vision (cs.CV) techniques such as image segmentation and convolutional neural networks. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) methods for improving segmentation performance. Finally, the paper uses synthetic data for pretraining, which is a common technique in neural network optimization (cs.NE).
